    "content": "<p>The effective stiffness of a cantilever beam of length L and flexural rigidity EI subjected to a transverse tip load W is</p>\n\n<img src=\"https://app-content.cdn.examgoal.net/fly/@width/image/jaoe38c1lz5hq0oh/13a53201-d27d-401d-944a-7ceb6315b665/6a39a610-4cd6-11ef-b0f4-1d4702540ce9/file-jaoe38c1lz5hq0oi.png?format=png\" data-orsrc=\"https://app-content.cdn.examgoal.net/image/jaoe38c1lz5hq0oh/13a53201-d27d-401d-944a-7ceb6315b665/6a39a610-4cd6-11ef-b0f4-1d4702540ce9/file-jaoe38c1lz5hq0oi.png\" loading=\"lazy\" style=\"max-width:100%;height:auto;display:block;margin:0 auto;max-height:40vh;vertical-align:baseline\" alt=\"GATE ME 2023 Strength of Materials - Deflection of Beams Question 1 English\">",
    "options": [
      {
        "identifier": "A",
        "content": "<span class=\"math-tex\">$\\rm \\frac{3El}{L^3}$</span>"
      },
      {
        "identifier": "B",
        "content": "<span class=\"math-tex\">$\\rm \\frac{2El}{L^3}$</span>"
      },
      {
        "identifier": "C",
        "content": "<span class=\"math-tex\">$\\rm \\frac{L^3}{2El}$</span>"
      },
      {
        "identifier": "D",
        "content": "<span class=\"math-tex\">$\\rm \\frac{L^3}{3EI}$</span>"
      }
    ],
    "correct_options": [
      "A"
    ],
    "explanation": "<p>$$ \\begin{aligned} & \\text { As we know, stiffness }=\\frac{\\text { Load }}{\\text { Deflection }} \\\\ & k=\\frac{W}{\\frac{W L^3}{3 E I}}=\\frac{3 E I}{L^3} \\end{aligned} $$</p>\n\n<p>Hence, the correct option is (A).</p>",
    "answer": null,
    "topic": null,
    "year": 2023,
    "yearKey": "gate-me-2023",
    "difficulty": null
  },
